{"tid":93580,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"岩岩差d死，個感覺真係..","createTime":"2017-01-24T13:50:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-24T14:01:50.000Z","uid":38961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cade4bccf24059771c24e4d2840eaaf4e4232e06","tid":93580,"uid":38961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T13:50:58.000Z","msg":"平時同d fd吹水成日講起「最多咪死，怕乜鳩啊」<br />\n<br />\n岩先小弟就返屋企，小弟歸家路程有幾個燈位加多一小段路，咁綠燈自然就過啦。<br />\n<br />\n點知個盲牛司機唔停，我一行出去，一段長響既咹聲沖我而黎，我拎過去一望，見到架車急煞，我向後跌低左，架車係我前面停左，我坐左係到呆左。<br />\n<br />\n我冇追究到個司機，慢慢行返屋企。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個刻就快俾車撞，我發現最多咪又係死，怕乜鳩姐，感覺死都係不外如是 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n不過跌低個下屎忽有d痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8c0c759c85a106261583cdfb50efd4189928609","tid":93580,"uid":75694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T13:59:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 勁"},{"pid":"903bc87b3e55ae2f872e7d342ea694eb7cfe9f8b","tid":93580,"uid":23785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T14:00:02.000Z","msg":"要還神 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7786161969bfbf21b4eee14e3bed47458ac4842d","tid":93580,"uid":75694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T14:01:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>要還神 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n差啲過唔到年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}